snippet.title: [HINDI] realme BGIS 2025 | SEMI FINALS - WEEK 02 | Day 4
snippet.description:
Dive into the heart of the battleground with realme BGIS 2025 SEMI FINALS Week 02! Witness 24 teams clash in a relentless pursuit of glory, but the first strongest 08 will advance to the Grand LAN Finals. snippet.title: Ek Date Aisi Bhi | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In Ek Date Aisi Bhi, join three friends as they set out on what they think will be the perfect romantic dates‚Ä¶ only for everything to go hilariously wrong! üò¨üíî
From awkward silences and weird restaurant choices to unexpected ex-encounters and disastrous conversations, each date turns into a comedy of errors. But just when all hope seems lost, a surprising twist brings unexpected connections and a dash of real love into the mix.
Full of laughs, relatable moments, and a sweet message, this sketch proves that sometimes, even the worst dates can lead to the best stories.‚ù§Ô∏è

snippet.title: Superman | Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
Krypto, take us home. #Superman - Only in Theaters July 11

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù will be in theaters and IMAX nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù will be in theaters and IMAX nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

#ArrangedMarriage #VishnuUnnikrishnan #ZeroFilter 

Arranged Marriage | Season 2 | Episode 2 | Ram Weds Janani | Vishnu Unnikrishnan | Rajiththa | Divya

Welcome to Arranged Marriage, a heartfelt YouTube series that explores love found in the most unexpected way‚Äîthrough an arranged marriage! Follow the journey of two individuals brought together by family, tradition, and culture, who slowly discover friendship, trust, and eventually, love. Watch how their worlds collide and connect as they navigate new experiences, overcome misunderstandings, and learn what it means to truly love and respect each other.

Welcome back to Arranged Marriage Season 2! üéâ In Episode 1, the much-awaited first night takes an unexpected turn when Janani, the newly wedded wife, gets her period at the most awkward moment. üò≥ Ram, her modern-gen husband, steps up and handles the situation with care, love, and understanding. From midnight medical shop runs to comforting moments, this episode beautifully explores how real love blossoms in unexpected situations. ‚ù§Ô∏è

‚úÖ Heartwarming First Night Moments

‚úÖ Unexpected Period Twist & Care
‚úÖ Romance, Laughter & Relatable Scenes

üëâ Don‚Äôt miss this emotional rollercoaster filled with love, care, and real-life relationship drama!

Each episode of Arranged Marriage delves into the beauty of growing affection and genuine connection, showcasing how relationships can blossom in surprising ways. If you enjoy stories of romance, personal growth, and cultural dynamics, subscribe and hit the notification bell for every chapter of this emotional and heartwarming tamil series.

snippet.description:
Being a NEET aspirant in India? It‚Äôs not just about books and mock tests‚Äîit's a whole emotional rollercoaster filled with anxiety, last-minute revision, relatives asking the wrong questions, and friends who mean well but say the weirdest things. üò©üìö

In this hilarious and painfully relatable FilterCopy sketch, we dive into the reality of a NEET student‚Äôs life‚Äîthe pressure, the panic, and of course, the people who keep saying things like:
üëâ ‚ÄúBeta, NEET nikaalna toh easy hai na?‚Äù
üëâ ‚ÄúArey Sharma ji ka beta bhi kar raha hai!‚Äù
üëâ ‚ÄúTumhe toh doctor banne ka passion hai na?‚Äù üòê

From group studies that turn into therapy sessions to panic before results day, this one‚Äôs for all the NEET warriors out there fighting their way through syllabus, stress, and society. üò≠‚úä

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. Episode 4346: Gokuldham Ki Holi
--------------------------------------------------------
Gokuldham Society comes together to celebrate Holika Dahan with great fervor, followed by lively Holi celebrations.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Episode No - 4346
Produced By - Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:  https://www.youtube.com/playlist?
list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

-----
Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

Star Cast: Deepika Singh, Shubham Dipta, Naman Shaw, Upadhyay Urvashi,Vipul Tyagi

This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant.
